<plot>Living alone in a small house in the woods, a blind woman goes about her daily routine. She feeds her cats, does her dishes, takes a shower... the whole time not realizing she isn't alone. A burglar ascends on the house, slowly making his way through the home. He suspects that he is too alone in the house, not hearing anything around him...because he is deaf.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?267995</url></doc>
